de.lambeck.pned.models.data.validation

Class AllNodesOnPathsValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lambeck.pned.models.data.validation.AbstractValidator
      • de.lambeck.pned.models.data.validation.AllNodesOnPathsValidator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IValidator

    public class AllNodesOnPathsValidator
extends AbstractValidator
    Checks that all nodes are on a path between the start place and the end place. To be used in combination with the ValidationController.
    Author:
    Thomas Lambeck, 4128320
